            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "保利置業半年純利跌44.3% 負債比率微降至75.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">保利置業(00119)公布，上半年公司擁有人應佔溢 利2.08億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年倒退44.3%；維持不派中期息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"保利置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"保利置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">保利置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內收入184.44億元，按年增48.1%。保利置業連同合營企業及聯營公司完成合約銷售267億元，按年減少6%，均價每股平方米27763元，按年升9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至6月底時，公司尚未償還的銀行及其他借貸(包括應付票據)為682.04億元，資產負債比率降至75.9%，較去年底時降0.7個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215091-%e4%bf%9d%e5%88%a9%e7%bd%ae%e6%a5%ad%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c44-3-%e8%b2%a0%e5%82%b5%e6%af%94%e7%8e%87%e5%be%ae%e9%99%8d%e8%87%b375-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240604_FI_source-web_00119.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 13:05:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "招商局港口中期盈利跌逾19%　股息維持25港仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">招商局港口(00144)公布，上半年盈利35.8億元，按年跌逾19%，中期息維持每股0.25元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：招商局港口官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250331_FI_source-web_00144-SZ-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商局港口官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250331_FI_source-web_00144-SZ-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：招商局港口官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團上半年經常利潤36.4億元，來自港口業務的經常利潤42.2億元，兩者跌12%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上半年收入升逾11%至64.6億元，完成集裝箱吞吐量升逾4%至7485萬個標準箱，散雜貨吞吐量則跌逾4%至2.6億噸。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215151-%e6%8b%9b%e5%95%86%e5%b1%80%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%a3%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be19%e3%80%80%e8%82%a1%e6%81%af%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%8125%e6%b8%af%e4%bb%99-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230830_FI_source-we00144_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 13:05:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "固生堂半年純利增41.9% 每股中期息增1.69倍 另斥最多3億港元回購",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">固生堂(02273)公布，上半年母公司擁有人應佔溢利1.52億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增41.9%；擬派中期息每股0.35港元，按年增1.69倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"固生堂官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/02273-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"固生堂官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/02273-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">固生堂官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，該公司又公布，董事會今日已決議行使回購授權，適時於公開市場購回公司股份，總價最多3億港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至6月底，該公司現金及現金等價物11.58億元，較去年底時增加3.7%。計息銀行貸款總額2.03億元，年利率介乎2.48%至2.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215006-%e5%9b%ba%e7%94%9f%e5%a0%82%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e41-9-%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e1-69%e5%80%8d-%e5%8f%a6%e6%96%a5%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a3%e5%84%84%e6%b8%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508029_FI_source-web_02273.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 12:45:28",
